                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/10252" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1535</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">269 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">突破与重构：反向并购助力并购双方铸就新篇章</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Breakthrough and Restructuring: Hanjia Design Skillfully Utilizes a Reverse Merger and Acquisition</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">许金花，刘梓鹏，温慧愉，左静璇</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">广东工业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">汉嘉设计集团股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">建筑、建材业与房地产业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">17 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">伏泰科技；汉嘉设计；反向并购；实践效果</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Hanjia Design Group Co.,Ltd., Suzhou Vortexinfo Technology CO.,LTD., Reverse Merger, Practice Effect</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">在产业变革加速的当下，反向并购开始成为企业实现业务突破与格局的有效途径。作为在建筑领域深耕多年的市政设计领头者汉嘉设计，在发展能力受制于行业环境的情况下，始终以战略眼光寻求突破自身局限；而专注于智慧市政与环境治理的伏泰科技，虽凭借技术优势在细分领域崭露头角，却受限于资本门槛难以快速扩大市场份额。双方基于高度的战略互补性，选择通过反向并购路径实现整合。在反向并购过程中，双方企业通过资产同步置换、巧妙定价等方式，有效规避了传统并购中常见的部分风险，并购后的协同效应显著。本案例详细剖析了本次反向并购的战略动因、交易结构设计的关键环节及其在业绩成果与协同效应创造等方面的实践效果，为学习产业变革背景下，科技企业如何借力资本市场实现数字创新突破、传统企业如何发挥反向并购优势重构战略资源提供实践参考。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">At a time when industrial transformation is accelerating, reverse takeovers have begun to become an effective way for enterprises to achieve business breakthroughs and pattern acquisitions. As a leader in municipal design in the field of architecture for many years, Hanjia Design has always sought to break through its own limitations with a strategic vision when its development ability is subject to the industry environment. Although Futai Technology, which focuses on smart municipal and environmental governance, has emerged in subdivided fields with its technological advantages, it is difficult to quickly expand its market share due to capital thresholds. Based on the high degree of strategic complementarity, the two parties chose to achieve integration through the reverse takeover path. In the process of reverse acquisition, the two companies effectively avoided some of the common risks in traditional mergers and acquisitions through synchronous asset replacement and clever pricing, and the synergy effect after the acquisition was significant. This case analyzes in detail the strategic motivations of this reverse takeover, the key links of transaction structure design, and its practical effects in terms of performance results and synergy creation, and provides practical reference for studying how technology enterprises can leverage the capital market to achieve digital innovation breakthroughs and how traditional enterprises can leverage the advantages of reverse takeovers to reconstruct strategic resources in the context of industrial transformation.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务管理理论与实务课程》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">并购动因理论；效率理论；协同效应理论；并购整合风险</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-12</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
